#This is a test of GFM for javascript

It should render the following:

* json
* javascript

```javascript
(function() {
  console.log('oh hai');  
}());
```

It will also render `json` blocks

```json
{
  "config": 34,
  "files": ["1.js", "2.js"]
}
```
